{
  "stem": "7506.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When we got out, which then was the middle-- I later learned-- the middle of the camp Westerbork, there were lots of people walking around, all over the place.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was damp.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Not really streets.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was more like hard and soft earth.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Dark in color, because that part of Holland is very dark, the earth is very dark.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And a lot of people, people with arm bands of different kinds.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I don't recall seeing Germans.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I do recall seeing what is named in Holland called the [FOREIGN LANGUAGE], which is blue uniforms.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I would compare it maybe, here, I don't quite know, really.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It's not really the police.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It is more than the police.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It is probably-- in Germany, you would call it [FOREIGN LANGUAGE].",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It's not just the ordinary police.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "It's more than the police.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "It's like in Spain would call it the [FOREIGN LANGUAGE].",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "It's more than just police.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They are the ones that guarded the camp.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they were what?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Dutch.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were all Dutch.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were not Germans.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were Dutch.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "People told us, this is Westerbork in the province of Drenthe.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And as I said earlier, from school I knew where Drenthe was.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's very near the Dutch border.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it's northeast Holland.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There's only two other provinces north of that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So it's a place that I would never have gone, and never-- I knew about it, that's all.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, I knew what it was very soon.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The reason I knew what it was very soon was that people were put on transport from there.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "People were-- they would come around the barrack with a list and call a person's name.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
